I don't know why some of the reviewers say the recipe needs salt. Maybe it was edited after those comments, but it includes 1.5 tablespoons of salt, not including any salting of the pasta water. It's just not listed in the ingredients, it's listed in the instructions. I often salt my food, but I did not need to with this recipe, which was enjoyed by all who tasted it. The really tedious part is arranging all the pasta in a layer, but otherwise it's a fairly simple recipe that tastes fantastic.

